      "time": 36.357,
      "time_str": "00:36.357",
      "text": "只是因为在人群中 多看了你一眼",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.009,
      "time_str": "00:44.009",
      "text": "再也没能忘掉你容颜",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 51.488,
      "time_str": "00:51.488",
      "text": "梦想着偶然能有一天再相见",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 58.778,
      "time_str": "00:58.778",
      "text": "从此我开始孤单思念",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
